All Implemented Interfaces:
IMergeCriterionAware, IMergeOptionAware, IMerger, IMerger2
public class AdditiveConflictMerger
extends ConflictMerger
This specific implementation of AbstractMerger will be used to merge conflicts in an additive merge context.

3.4
